caption.text:
Imagine you average 2,000 views on your Reels.

*As a small IG account...*

This means you can get 50-100 leads per month if you promote your content well.

Out of these 50-100 leads, 5-10 will become customers.

Question:

How much do you want these people to pay you—$50 or $3,000?

That’s why a high-ticket offer is better than a low-ticket offer.

Because you can make way more, often without sacrificing sales conversion.

Comment “CALCULATOR” and I’ll DM you my new IG calculator that will show you how much money you can make with your account today.

caption.text:
Take a guess in the comments 💰

1️⃣ 10k followers won’t make you six figures a year.

You might have low engagement, or maybe you’ve changed your niche, meaning those followers aren’t as valuable anymore since you’re getting low views anyway.

2️⃣ One viral reel that gets 10k comments won’t make you six figures either…

You might gain 1000+ new followers, and that’s about it.
If it was on a consistent basis then it would be 7 figures a year for sure!

3️⃣ But averaging 10k views per reel can make you six figures a year!

How?

If you average 10k views per reel, you could generate 500 leads monthly (based on a 5% conversion rate using a ManyChat funnel).

Out of those 500 leads, if half are financially qualified and interested in your services, typically 10% will become customers.

So, if you charge $1,000 for your services and gain 25 customers, that’s $25k in revenue.

That’s how you can turn your views into clients and revenue!

Want to learn how to do this in detail? 

Comment the word MANYCHAT, and I’ll DM you the training for free now 🔥

caption.text:
4 things that work on Instagram today 👇

1. Consistency

If you can’t commit to posting for 1 year, you are more likely going to fail. 

Whether you do cold outreach, paid ads, or organic social media, they all take time before you see big results.

2. Shareable Content

Instagram’s CEO confirmed that shares are one of the most important metrics on Instagram today.

The more people share your content, the more views you will get.

One of my favorite types of shareable content is memes.

They help you reach more non-followers. These people engage with your content, and the next day, they see your educational expert content because of their previous interaction with your account.

Then they follow you.

3. Copy Popular Videos but Share Your Own Experience

The best strategy to grow these days is to find the TOP-30 reels in your niche and recreate them as accurately as possible.

The only thing you change is the content. 

If there is a talking video about how to lose weight, you take that video, copy the hook, transition, speed, and timing, but you share your own advice and experience.

4. Engagement Hacking

You want to get more engagement. More engagement = more leads. More leads = more sales.

Higher engagement is the best way to turn followers into paying customers.

Comment “ENGAGEMENT,” and I’ll DM you my PDF with the TOP-18 hacks that will boost your engagement on reels and stories 🔥

caption.text:
This year Instagram revealed a new official guide on how to grow on Instagram with reels in 2024.

It’s an 84-page document with different content ideas and tips.

C0mment “PDF,” and I’ll DM you the guide right now.

I also chose 6 most interesting tips from it and recorded my feedback: You will find them there.
